entries.title_d: As a test of commitment, the Cloak Representative has sent you on a mission to acquire CorSec transport security codes. CorSec Command has been monitoring your communications and has sent a transport to meet you with false codes. You can give these codes to the Cloak representative without fear of compromising CorSec security.
entries.title: Corellia System: Acquire CorSec Security Codes for the Cloaks
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the provided navigation waypoint and await the return of the Cloak Representative.
entries.quest_rendezvous1_d: Travel to the navigation waypoint and meet with the CorSec transport that CorSec Command has sent to meet you.
entries.quest_location_d: The CorSec transport is slated to meet you elsewhere in the Corellia system.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the Cloak Representative and transmit to him the falsified security codes.
entries.quest_dock1_d: Dock with the transport to acquire the falsified codes. This should also make this operation look belivable to any Cloak ships that may be observing.
entries.hello_p: Initiating secure channel. Hello pilot. We've got some falsified security codes for you. Dock up whenever you're ready.
entries.hello_d: Greetings, CorSec. Have you returned with the security codes? Begin your docking sequence.
entries.found_loc_p: Secure channel open. We have received your mission update. We are sending a CorSec transport to this location. They will transmit false security codes for you.
entries.found_loc_d: Secure channel open. Scans are clear. Proceed to this location, dock with the Cloak rep, and transfer the false codes to him.
entries.failed_destroyed: Looks like this mission is a wash. Go ahead and come back to the station for debriefing.
entries.docking_started_pickup: Transferring security codes. Preparing dock sequence.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Docking request received. Begin your security code transfer.
entries.docking_complete_pickup: Docking clamps are clear. Good luck, pilot.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Good, pilot, good. We will be in touch soon. Now return to your Station, but mention none of this to CorSec Command.
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer: <\#pcontrast3  Warning. Enemy craft inbound.\#pcontrast1 >
entries.arrived_at_pickup: Secure channel open. Dock with a CorSec transport here and they will upload some unused security codes.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Secure channel open. You are cleared to dock with the Cloak representative and transmit the false codes.
